ore you stop taking Propecia, as you can lose any hair that you gained within the last 9 — 12 months if you stop treatment. These is currently no evidence to suggest that Propecia will interact with minoxidil, which is another hair loss treatment that is found in Regaine, but you should still speak to a medical professional before using these two medications together.</p><p>Generic medicines contain the same active ingredient and are equally effective and equivalent as the branded products but are available at a lower price. Buy Propecia online with confidence knowing that you are getting the very best quality, service and value. Propecia is used to treat male pattern hair loss, a common condition in men where the scalp hair thins and can result in a receding hairline or a balding at the top of the buy finasteride propecia. It contains finasteride as its active ingredient, which belongs to the type II 5-alpha reductase inhibitors class of medications. Finasteride inhibits the enzyme 5-alpha reductase that normally converts testosterone to a hormone known as DHT dihydrotestosterone that causes a decrease in hair growth and thinning of the hair.</p>


